I reported it on seamless (cause your girl ain’t rich to be spending on mistakes and letting things like this slide) and lord and behold 2 hours later the restaurant calls me. (Did I mention I come here a lot?) I know the people that work there and I know the person who called me, you see the reviews that say this “lady that picked up and was rude” on the google review section. yes that was her. Now that’s not it, upon writing this review I am currently suffering from a good old stomach bug from the food I ingested earlier today.
